WELCOME TO THE RITZ LOUNGE!
We strive to be the best bar in Jacksonville Beach, Florida. Our bar staff are knowledgeable and eager to please our patrons and guests. We are a full service bar and serve over 400 cocktails and shooters. We are proud to be "A Great Place to Meet" since opening our doors in 1945!
All of our patrons must be 21+ with a valid state issued ID.
Phone
(904) 246-2255
Location
185 3rd Ave. North
Jacksonville Beach, FL 32250
Hours
MON-FRI
1pm-2am
SAT & SUN
